ub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=183.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Competitiveness</span><hr size=1> First let me say this... Thanks for taking all the fun out of calling you guys out... lol.... instead you participated in a real discussion and debate.. kudos.. <br>
<br>
